<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>conido株式会社</title>

<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
<link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />

<meta property="og:title" content="conido株式会社"/>
<meta property="og:description" content="人口変動に左右されない、持続可能なインフラを。"/>
<meta property="og:image" content="/images/ogp.png"/>
<meta property="og:type" content="website"/>
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"/>

<style>
*{
  box-sizing:border-box;
}

html{
  scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
  margin:0;
  font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;
  color:#111;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}

a{
  color:inherit;
  text-decoration:none;
}

/* ===== HEADER ===== */
header{
  position:fixed;
  top:0;
  width:100%;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.92);
  backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
  z-index:100;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.05);
}

.nav{
  max-width:1400px;
  margin:auto;
  padding:20px 72px;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
}

.logo{
  font-size:28px;
  font-weight:900;
  letter-spacing:-0.04em;
  flex-shrink:0;
}

nav{
  display:flex;
  gap:44px;
  align-items:center;
}

nav a{
  color:#111;
  font-size:15px;
}

.contact,
.button,
.footer-button{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:14px 24px;
  background:#0f766e;
  color:#fff !important;
  border-radius:14px;
  font-weight:700;
  white-space:nowrap;
}

/* ===== HERO ===== */
.hero{
  min-height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  padding:180px 72px 140px;
  background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.55), rgba(255,255,255,.62)),
    url("/images/membrane.jpeg");
  background-size:cover;
  background-position:center;
}

.container{
  max-width:1400px;
  margin:auto;
  width:100%;
}

h1{
  font-size:clamp(52px,6vw,80px);
  line-height:1.12;
  letter-spacing:-0.04em;
  margin-bottom:32px;
  font-weight:800;
  word-break:keep-all;
}

.hero p{
  font-size:clamp(19px,2vw,24px);
  line-height:1.9;
  max-width:38em;
}

/* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
.section{
  padding:180px 72px;
}

.label{
  color:#0f766e;
  font-weight:700;
  margin-bottom:12px;
}

h2{
  font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,60px);
  margin-bottom:56px;
}

.cards{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:56px;
}

.card{
  display:block;
  background:white;
  border-radius:28px;
  overflow:hidden;
  box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
  transform:translateY(-6px);
}

.card img{
  width:100%;
  height:360px;
  object-fit:cover;
  display:block;
}

.card-body{
  padding:44px;
}

.card-body ul{
  padding-left:20px;
  line-height:2;
}

/* ===== COMPANY ===== */
.company{
  background:#f8fbfb;
}

.company-box{
  background:white;
  padding:64px;
  border-radius:32px;
  max-width:760px;
  width:100%;
  box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

.company-name{
  font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,36px);
  font-weight:900;
  margin-bottom:24px;
}

.company-text{
  line-height:2.2;
  font-size:clamp(15px,2vw,18px);
}

/* ===== FOOTER ===== */
footer{
  padding:140px 40px;
  text-align:center;
}

img{
  max-width:100%;
  height:auto;
  display:block;
}

/* ===== MOBILE ===== */
@media(max-width:900px){

  .nav{
    padding:14px 20px;
    flex-direction:row;
    gap:0;
  }

  .logo{
    font-size:22px;
  }

  nav{
    gap:14px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    justify-content:flex-end;
  }

  nav a{
    font-size:13px;
  }

  .contact{
    padding:10px 14px;
    font-size:13px;
    border-radius:10px;
  }

  .hero{
    padding:120px 20px 80px;
    min-height:auto;
  }

  .section{
    padding:100px 20px;
  }

  .cards{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
  }

  .card img{
    height:260px;
  }

  .company-box{
    padding:32px 24px;
    max-width:100%;
    border-radius:20px;
  }

  footer{
    padding:80px 20px;
  }
}

@media(max-width:480px){
  nav a:not(.contact){
    display:none;
  }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <div class="nav">
    <div class="logo">conido</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#company">会社概要</a>
      <a href="/vision">私たちの想い</a>
      <a href="/products/jokaso-dx">プロダクト</a>
      <a href="/news">ニュース</a>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfCwxhrTMIHNpyX9h5-PlJ1SnbsK03lYNtL2lojUg3hFGoSkg/viewform?usp=header"
         class="contact" target="_blank">お問い合わせ</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>
      人口変動に左右されない、<br>
      持続可能なインフラを。
    </h1>
    <p>
      人口変動に依存しない地域基盤の実現を目指し、<br>
      conido株式会社は分散型インフラに取り組みます。
    </p>
    <a href="/vision" class="button" style="margin-top:48px;">私たちの想い</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="service" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">Business</div>
    <h2>事業内容</h2>

    <div class="cards">
      <a href="/products/jokaso-dx" class="card">
        <img src="/images/sensor.png" alt="浄化槽管理DX" />
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>浄化槽管理DX</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>浄化槽管理士資格を保有</li>
            <li>浄化槽管理Webアプリを開発</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/products/jokaso-dx" class="card">
        <img src="/images/membrane.jpeg" alt="分散型インフラ研究" />
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>分散型インフラ研究</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>浄化槽による分散化のゾーニング提案</li>
            <li>将来的な膜処理の検討</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="company" class="section company">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">Company</div>
    <h2>会社概要</h2>
    <div class="company-box">
      <div class="company-name">conido株式会社</div>
      <div class="company-text">
        代表取締役 石井ゆめみ<br><br>
        〒010-0041<br>
        秋田県秋田市広面字赤沼20-6
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfCwxhrTMIHNpyX9h5-PlJ1SnbsK03lYNtL2lojUg3hFGoSkg/viewform?usp=header"
     class="footer-button" target="_blank">お問い合わせはこちら</a>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
